{"tid":1316394,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"代post: 教育長輩，係有成果既","createTime":"2019-07-14T15:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:06:32.000Z","uid":89184,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c3fc62dae7b8490b1bb8304166933dfd2eef59f6","tid":1316394,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"代post，<br />\n<br />\n我朋友個朋友既父母，唔太識上網，只係睇下cctvb，偶爾上下fb<br />\n<br />\n教育程度低，不嬲唔太明白d時事，以前仲覺得搞事暴力好唔岩<br />\n<br />\n經過朋友解釋事情背景、經過，同埋幫佢follow 多d 唔同既fb pages 同groups （呢個好重要！），<br />\n<br />\n依家終於明白事理，仲支持香港市民了<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到大家打打氣，教育工作係慢長，但仍然係有用既！<br />\n<br />\n文宣巴打絲打，加油呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RVMTmN5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRVMTmN5.jpg&h=a37b41b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d1kQo1r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1kQo1r.jpg&h=0d035723&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9c0ddf1ef74db889b38d66973fcfc246610344c","tid":1316394,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:59:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8e5b24db7823b233fd5252d0355a0199da2ea60d","tid":1316394,"uid":10541,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:00:13.000Z","msg":"加油，要俾啲心機感受自己老豆老母<br />\n咁樣佢地落街買餸食早餐無咁意俾人誤導<br />\n仲分分鐘會屌到其他師奶都企我地個邊"},{"pid":"b7f6094e6f99433c7d8ed3f99187e4503469ac95","tid":1316394,"uid":10541,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e5b24db7823b233fd5252d0355a0199da2ea60d","tid":1316394,"uid":10541,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:00:13.000Z","msg":"加油，要俾啲心機感受自己老豆老母<br />\n咁樣佢地落街買餸食早餐無咁意俾人誤導<br />\n仲分分鐘會屌到其他師奶都企我地個邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"感化*"},{"pid":"7c1b429af53fd92fa93cdf0b5a9ecea758588781","tid":1316394,"uid":55563,